caption:
I got FAT in Seattle.

Came home and decided something had to give. 

6 months later, my problem is you can’t tell me I ain’t Devin Haney in the gym. 😩😂😎🥴. 

Anyway, I hope this encourages you to know you can change whatever you don’t like if you stay committed long enough🫶🏽. And if you don’t got the patience girl go ahead and lay on that table. As the American poet Tupac Shakur once wrote, “I ain’t mad at’cha” 😜🫡
